docs {
  # Enrollments

  Manages student enrollments into course instances.

  ## Endpoints

  | Method | Path                                          | Description              |
  |--------|-----------------------------------------------|--------------------------|
  | POST   | /api/v1/enrollments                           | Enroll a student         |
  | GET    | /api/v1/course-instances/:id/enrollments      | List enrollments         |
  | PUT    | /api/v1/enrollments/:instanceID/:userID       | Update enrollment        |

  ## Business Rules
  - Student must belong to the batch that owns the course instance
  - Duplicate enrollments are rejected (409 Conflict)
  - Allowed statuses: Enrolled, Dropped, Completed, Failed

  ## Key Variables
  - {{COURSE_INSTANCE_ID}}  — set by "Create Course Instance"
  - {{ENROLLMENT_USER_ID}} — set by "Enroll Student"
}
